=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />米糠油</span></span><br />\nHKTV mall 有好多款不同産地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVJhyre.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVJhyre.png&h=df86e731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n米糠油，有獨特的抗氧化力、耐高溫<br />\n<br />\n日本著名腦科醫學博士山嶋哲盛為大家推薦的健康植物油中，米糠油是其中一種。米糠油又稱為米油、玄米油，是如今在日本很受歡迎的食用油。<br />\n<br />\n它是由糙米的糠皮提煉成的油脂，是世界公認的營養極為豐富，抗氧化力最強的植物油之一，耐高溫、不易產生毒素，非常適合煎炒油炸，是與橄欖油相媲美的高級健康植物油。"},{"pid":"d4deb53bac6bf22178c03cb4b930abe461bfae98","tid":1828222,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T16:14:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以follow 埋呢幾個 ig page</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/anywherebutchina?igshid=1pzh9252og8uj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fanywherebutchina%3Figshid%3D1pzh9252og8uj&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=89dfd3c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/anywherebutchina?igshid=1pzh9252og8uj</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/con.sharehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcon.sharehk&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=5c2c284f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/con.sharehk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yellow_ribbon_catering\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyellow_ribbon_catering&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=afdc7de4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/yellow_ribbon_catering</a>"},{"pid":"265a4495caa2371c854155ee2e23ee56525a2030","tid":1828222,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislik